  "about_item": [
    "🐾【Waterproof & Easy to Clean】Designed with a waterproof outer cover and an internal barrier lining to fully protect the foam core, this dog bed resists spills and accidents. The removable, machine-washable cover ensures hassle-free cleaning, making it ideal for everyday use and active pets.",
    "🦴【Orthopedic Comfort & Joint Support】Featuring medical-grade egg-crate foam, the bed evenly distributes your dog’s weight, reducing pressure points and supporting joint health. Ideal for pets of all ages, especially those with mobility needs or joint concerns, it offers restorative, comfortable sleep every night.",
    "🌱【Premium, Eco-Friendly Materials】Made with ultra-soft, non-toxic fabrics and environmentally conscious filling that hold their shape over time. The high-quality construction is gentle on your pet and the planet, ensuring lasting coziness and peace of mind.",
    "🐕【Perfect Fit for Every Dog】Available in three convenient sizes—L (36\"x27\"x3\") for dogs up to 60 lbs, XL (42\"x29\"x4\") for dogs up to 100 lbs. Lightweight and durable, this bed is easy to move and provides comfort at home, in crates, during travel, or outdoors.",
    "🎁【Satisfaction Promise & Friendly Support】We are dedicated to your satisfaction with excellent quality and attentive customer care. If you have any questions, our team is always ready to assist and ensure you and your dog enjoy a wonderful experience."
  ],
