        "position": 4,
        "title": "NOT INDESTRUCTIBLE/NOT CHEW PROOF",
        "text": "This is not indestructible what so ever!!! My 25 pound Peekapoo(Cockapoo + Pekingese) chewed a hole in 5 minutes and destroyed this bed on the same day I got. Very disappointed in the description as I feel it is misleading. Anyhow, it was nice for the hour it lasted, looked comfy, but NOT INDESTRUCTIBLE.",
        "rating": 1,
        "date": "April 19, 2026",
        "author": "Amanda H20Man",
        "author_link": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AFWBR7FX77SPEQYQR5MHQOU7RHKQ",
        "author_image": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default.png",
