      {
        "position": 6,
        "title": "Dogs love these",
        "text": "We use a lot of these Sytopia dog beds, and this one fits right into our rotation in our facility. The dogs settle onto it immediately, and the support stays consistent throughout the day. The waterproof cover is practical for a busy, dog‑friendly environment and wipes clean with ease.The foam holds its shape well, even after repeated use, and the stitching has been reliable across every Sytopia bed we’ve tried. It’s lightweight enough to move around the facility but still sturdy enough for larger dogs to use comfortably.I am awarding this 5 stars for the following: dependable comfort, durable materials, easy cleaning, and consistent performance across daily use.",
