        "title": "Nice sturdy supportive bed. For my old dogs",
        "text": "I have several senior dogs and I’m always looking for supportive, comfortable beds for them, This one a tiny bit thin but they love it. They stretch out on it and zonk right out. And they wake up and they don’t seem as stiff and achy. That might be wishful thinking but they all love to sleep on it. I did get a cover for it because the fabric from which it is made it is made feels a bit scratchy. So I got a soft cover for it. They love it. And all the dogs are over 60 lbs so this is a nice big size for the boy dogs. I also like the bottom of the bed with the non skid fabric. It stays put and doesn’t slip around as they try to get comfortable. It’s totally worth the monthS",
